<p class="">Can the right hon. Gentleman say how many were due to mechanical power being used?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1f575bfa-7170-4b0f-ac48-b0aca64b042d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
